  "text": "The performance of the laser tunable by means of a PZT actuator is illustrated by Figs. (9) , [CITATION_1] , and [CITATION_2] . The laser produces frequency modulated signal with very little admixture of amplitude modulation. The modulation frequency can exceed a MHz, and the modulation magnitude can exceed tens of MHz. Tunability span of 3 GHz is demonstrated.",
